<h1>Manage Your Staff</h1>

<h2>Your Current Slaves (Total of <%= @got_people.count %>)</h2>
<p>Here's a list of people that are currently slaving away for your movies. You can click the individual person to view and edit the details or delete the person.</p>

<% if @got_people.count == 0 %>
    <ul class = "bullet_message">
      <li>You currently do not have anyone working on your movies.</li>
    </ul>
<% else %>
    <% @got_people.each do |person| %>
      <ul>
        <li><a href='/people/<%= person['id'] %>'><button>View details</button></a>
           <%= person['name'] %>: # tasks assinged</li>
      </ul>
    <% end %>
<% end %>

<br/>
<h2>Add More Person</h2>
<p>Click the button below to add more people to work on your movies!</p>
<p><a href='/people/new'><button>Add More Person</button></a></p>

